channel.title: Eclipse-Rsps V4 Finally Opened!
channel.description:
[center]ECLIPSE-RSPS V4[/center] Eclipse-Rsps V4 is now open for everyone to play. I invite everyone to come have a good time with me on this new RSPS. We have just opened and i currently have 12 online. Which isnt good but i wouldnt say its bad :P. I'm really just having this server online to have a good time and to have fun, so everyone is welcome to come play. [size=14pt]www.eclipse-rsps.nl.ae [/size]
[img]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s519/eclipse-rsps/1-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s519/eclipse-rsps/7-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s519/eclipse-rsps/6-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s519/eclipse-rsps/5-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s519/eclipse-rsps/4-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s519/eclipse-rsps/2-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s519/eclipse-rsps/3-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s519/eclipse-rsps/cahoti.png[/img] [img]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s519/eclipse-rsps/savee.png[/img] And yes we still need staff positions filled.
